WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Hello everyone from AC News!

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let’s watch an exclusive clip from the movie Se sei così ti dico di sì,

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.000
the new Eugenio Cappuccio comedy,

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:27.000
played by Emilio Solfrizzi, Iaia Forte and Belen Rodriguez.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:29.000
Piero Cicala is a ex-singer

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:32.000
who had his short moment of glory in the '80s, with one big hit.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:37.000
Now he lives a normal life in Fassano di Puglia;

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:39.000
but everything will change when he is selected

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:42.000
to participate in a TV show of old music glories.

